txt.en: DNT - 'Ah, you return! And with the furs as well.'
'Ah, you return! And with such fine furs and fangs as well.'
Nósni is in Hagbuth in north-east Clovengap.\n\nBring the furs and fangs to Nósni.

Clovengap mist-stalkers and sabre-tooth cats can be found in the vineyards.\n\nNósni has asked you to bring back furs from Clovengap mist-stalkers and fangs from the deadly sabre-tooth cats of Clovengap.

'If you will not be talked out of avoiding the beasts, you may as well do away with any you come across. Bring back their hides and fangs. The tailor, Klátha, will use the furs to clothe our warriors and families, while the deadly fangs make for good weapons.'
Beneath the crumbling arches of ancient vineyards prowls a deadly beast. Has the crystal corruption altered this already formidable foe?
